'''John Gerber''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

Gerber was inducted into the [[American Contract Bridge League]]'s Hall of Fame in 1998.<ref>{{cite web 
 | title = Hall of Fame
 | author = 
 | publisher = ACBL
 | url = http://www.acbl.org/about/hall-of-fame/members/20
 | date = 
 | accessdate = 2014-10-19 }}</ref>

